                  </hi>. I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">Read: "Chelmsford Quarter Session; Daniel Gilson, Convicted, June, 1854, of stealing live fowls; Confined Three Months"</hi>)—I heard him tried—the prisoner is the person.</p>
               <p>
